name: The Trees and The Life #005-Violet Hill
description:
It's not too tall but it's enough for us to feel the cold, and it was really cold. There was first-timer and second-timer. Daisy flower field greeted us with its dew, clouds blew onto our faces. From afar a tall dry tree stands tall on a violet hill, maybe it's the hill's longest resident. We just passed by and show our respect.

The Trees and The Life is a 10-Photo-Based-NFT Collection made by Danar Tri Atmojo. As the first-ever collection made, Danar dedicated these NFT's to mother nature as we move towards the new era of digitalization using Tezos blockchain as #CleanNFTs.
